Package: vmronly
Type: Package
Title: VM-Restricted Access to Microsoft Fabric
Version: 1.0.0
Author: UZIMA Data Team
Maintainer: Derick Imbati <derick.imbati@aku.edu>
Description: Provides secure, VM-locked access to Microsoft Fabric Lakehouse 
    for authorized researchers. Enforces VM-only execution, Windows-based 
    authentication, per-user table permissions, and VM-only data downloads.
